Captain Eddie Rickenbacker
announces a new concept of
air transportation
I am happy to announce a great new achievement in air
travel. Eastern Air Lines again demonstrates its leadership
with the introduction of the newest, fastest, quietest, most
luxurious airliner ever built -the Golden Falcon...DC-7B,
produced to our specifications by the Douglas Aircraft
Company, Inc.
The Golden Falcon is truly a magic carpet of luxury aloft.
Every detail of this magnificent airliner has been engineered
to insure the security and comfort of our passengers.
I am sure that every air traveler will find in this quieter,
more luxurious airliner a comfort never before experienced.
I invite you to fly the Golden Falcon and enjoy for yourself
all the advantages of this new leader in air transportation.
